@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "OpenClaw Gateway" #FFF3E0 {

  package "Dynamic Prompt Context" #FFEBEE {
    [workspace/\n(AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, SKILLS.md)] as Workspace #FFCDD2
  }

  package "Session & Subscription" #E3F2FD {
    [Event Subscriber] as Hooks #BBDEFB
    [Web UI / Chat Channels] as UI #BBDEFB
  }

  package "Pi Agent Runtime (Embedded pi-mono)" #E8F5E9 {
    [Reasoning & Execution Loop] as Reasoning #C8E6C9
    [SessionManager\n(JSONL History & Auto-compaction)] as SessionManager #C8E6C9
    [System Prompt Builder\n(Bundles the 'Menu')] as PromptBuilder #C8E6C9

    package "Tool Injection Pipeline" #FFF9C4 {
      [Base Tools\n(Read, Write, Bash)] as BaseTools #FFF59D
      [OpenClaw Tools\n(Browser, OS Sensors, etc.)] as CustomTools #FFF59D
      BaseTools ..> CustomTools : Overridden by
    }
  }

  [LLM Providers\n(Anthropic, OpenAI, etc.)] as LLM #E1BEE7
}

Workspace --> PromptBuilder : Injects text guides (Skills)
CustomTools --> PromptBuilder : Injects JSON definitions (Tools)
PromptBuilder --> Reasoning : Packs System Payload

Reasoning <--> LLM : API Calls & Stream
Reasoning <--> CustomTools : Executes Tools
Reasoning <--> SessionManager : Reads/Writes History

Reasoning --> Hooks : Emits Events
Hooks --> UI : Streams Chunks
@enduml
